    "TigerBot pretrain zh focuses on web content, encyclopedias, books, and language texts.",
    "Apart from the common Chinese and English corpora, the Beijing Academy of Artificial Intelligence collaborates with other institutions to build the largest opensource Arabic pre-training corpus globally, known as ArabicText 2022 24.",
